# agent-skills.config — which upstream skills to vendor into this repo.
#
# One skill name per line. Lines starting with '#' are comments; blank lines are
# ignored. A single line of '*' (or 'all') selects every skill upstream offers.
#
# On each `agent-skills-sync` run, the skills listed here are vendored under the
# prefix (default vendor/agent-skills/skills/), and any vendored skill NOT listed
# here is deleted. This file is the single source of truth for what you keep.
#
# This file is yours: the sync tool seeds it once (defaulting to all skills) and
# never overwrites it again. Edit it, then re-run the sync to apply.
#
# To pin a subset, replace the '*' below with explicit names, e.g.:
#   pr-review
#   address-pr-comments

*
